XMap README file

Module Purpose
Xoops Module that makes use of Google Maps Public API to graphicaly show the site's members in the world map. Can Zoom In, Zoom Out, Pan, etc...

Installation Procedures:
.Extract the tarball in the XOOPS_ROOT_PATH
.Set permissions in modules/xmap acording to your security policy (RX should be enough)
.In Xoops Admin Section, just install XMap module

Update Procedures:
.Replace module files extracting the tarball in the XOOPS_ROOT_PATH over your existing XMap version
.Check file permissions in modules/xmap acording to your security policy (RX should be enough)
.In Xoops Admin Section, update your XMap module.
.Check replaced/updated blocks


